ddf.catalog.content.operation

Interface StorageRequest

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Operation, Request, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CreateStorageRequest, DeleteStorageRequest, ReadStorageRequest, UpdateStorageRequest
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CreateStorageRequestImpl, DeleteStorageRequestImpl, ReadStorageRequestImpl, UpdateStorageRequestImpl

    public interface StorageRequest
extends Request
    Base request interface for storage operations. This code is experimental. While this interface is functional and tested, it may change or be removed in a future version of the library.

        String getId()
        Returns the unique ID associated with this storage request. The ID should be used by the StorageProvider to StorageProvider.commit(StorageRequest) or StorageProvider.rollback(StorageRequest) changes.

        ID
